name: D’Arch: Chapter II
description:
What is time when you found “the one”? It seems impossible to keep track of it, sometimes it stays still, other times it flies without you even noticing. Everything feels right when you found your person and the only issue you have with time is that it will eventually run out and you’ll be thrown back into your loneliness again. So for how long will this fairytale last?

To be continued…
